  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\nLast row in \"Description\" is overlapped by \"Save\" button, so user cannot see what he types. Scrolling to the bottom fixes text in the same state, so \"Save\" button covers last row.\r\n\r\n\"Predictive\" option on IPhone settings  should be enabled.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\"Save\" button does not overlap last row, \"Description\" is shown correctly\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nLast row in \"Description\"  is overlapped by \"Save\"\r\n\r\n### Prerequisites\r\n- \"Predictive\" option should be enabled (Settings > General > Keyboard)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Login with existing account\r\n- Open Profile\r\n- Tap on Edit\r\n- Fill up \"Description\" (more than 4 rows)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: 0.9.12\r\n\r\n* Operating System: IOS 10.3.2\r\n\r\n*Device: IPhone 5s\r\n\r\n![txt](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/33398967/32740119-93e37dfe-c8aa-11e7-968b-1937f198a34b.png)\r\n",
